data.description: **Seller is offering $2,000 in closing cost assist with acceptable offer** Welcome to your dream home with breathtaking water views!  This stunning townhouse offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and natural beauty.  With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and a host of desirable features, this newer build townhome is a must-see.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the elegant tile flooring that flows throughout the main living area.  The spacious open plan kitchen and family room provide an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertainment.  The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops accented by dark cabinetry throughout.  One of the highlights of this townhouse is tranquil water views both from the main living area and the primary bedroom. Why wait for a new build when this gorgeous home is ready for new owners. Conveniently located, the Meadows at Oakleaf, is an energy star community that offers its residents a pool, playground and dog park.  It is ideally situated close to shopping and restaurants.  Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful townhouse your next home.  Schedule a preview today!
